summary: Comprehensive frontend testing of 3 new features completed successfully: 1) Role-based access control with Settings page, 2) Time-period based report export for coaches, 3) Auto-fill date when planning session from calendar. All features working as expected.
passed_tests: Settings page (/settings) loads correctly with Profile and Role sections
Role selection shows Coach Developer and Coach options with proper styling
Coach Developer role option is selectable with blue highlight
Coach role option is selectable with green highlight and shows 'Link to Coach Profile' dropdown
User name input field works correctly
Save Settings button saves settings and shows success toast
Settings persist and show current user status at bottom of page
Calendar page (/calendar) loads with monthly view and navigation
Calendar day selection works - clicking a day highlights it and shows sidebar
Calendar sidebar shows selected date (e.g., 'Sunday, 25 Jan')
Calendar sidebar 'Plan Session' button navigates to /session/new with date parameter
Session Setup page (/session/new?date=YYYY-MM-DD) auto-fills the date input field
Session Setup shows 'This session will be marked as planned' message when date is set
Coach Profile page has Reports tab accessible via data-testid='tab-reports'
Reports tab shows Start Date and End Date pickers
Reports tab shows Quick Select buttons (Last 7 Days, Last 30 Days, Last 3 Months, Year to Date)
Quick Select buttons auto-fill date range correctly
Report Preview section appears when dates are selected showing period and session count
Export PDF button (data-testid='export-pdf-btn') is present and enables when dates selected
Export CSV button (data-testid='export-csv-btn') is present and enables when dates selected
Export buttons show proper error toast when no completed sessions in date range
Header 'Plan Session' button navigates without date (expected behavior)
Sidebar 'Plan Session' button navigates with date parameter (expected behavior)
seed_data_creation: Created test coaches during testing (Test Coach, Test Coach 2) - stored in browser local storage
context_for_next_testing_agent: All 3 requested features are working correctly: 1) Settings page at /settings with role selection (Coach Developer vs Coach), 2) Coach Profile Reports tab with date range pickers and PDF/CSV export buttons, 3) Calendar to Session Setup date auto-fill via URL parameter. The app uses browser local storage so data doesn't persist between browser sessions. To test report export with actual data, first create a coach, then create and complete an observation session for that coach.
